{"type":"message","id":"1a1e8442","parentId":"67e649e1","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:25:28.438Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_vhkhldv0qyp76fawyie20reu","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can use \"skillhub install [skill]\" to install.\ndesktop-control  Desktop Control\n  - Advanced desktop automation with mouse, keyboard, and screen control\n高级桌面自动化，支持鼠标、键盘和屏幕控制\n  - version: 1.0.0\ndesktop-control-win  Desktop Control (Windows)\n  - Control desktop applications on Windows — launch, close, focus, resize, move windows, simulate keyboard/mouse input, manage processes, control VSCode, read clipboard, and capture screen info. Use when the user wants to interact with any running program, switch windows, type text, press shortcuts, open files in VSCode, manage running processes, or get system display information.\n控制Windows桌面应用，支持窗口管理（启动、关闭、聚焦、调整、移动）、模拟键鼠输入、进程管理、VSCode操控、剪贴板读取及屏幕捕获。适用于程序交互、窗口切换、文本输入、快捷键操作、文件打开、进程管理及获取系统显示信息。\n  - version: 1.0.1\ndesktop-control-1-0-0  Desktop Control 1.0.0\n  - Advanced desktop automation with mouse, keyboard, and screen control\nAdvanced desktop automation with mouse, keyboard, and screen control\n  - version: 1.0.0\nmacos-desktop-control  MacOS Desktop Control (Mouse, Keyboard, Screenshots)\n  - Automate macOS desktop by capturing screenshots and executing precise mouse movements, clicks, and keyboard inputs via cliclick.\nAutomate macOS desktop by capturing screenshots and executing precise mouse movements, clicks, and keyboard inputs via cliclick.\n  - version: 1.0.0\norgo-desktop-control  Orgo Desktop Control\n  - Provision and control Orgo cloud computers using the orgo_client Python SDK. Use when launching remote desktops, automating browsers, running bash/python rem...\nProvision and control Orgo cloud computers using the orgo_client Python SDK. Use when launching remote desktops, automating browsers, running bash/python rem...\n  - version: 1.0.2\nwindows-desktop-control  Windows 桌面控制\n  - Windows 桌面控制工具 (仅Windows) - 截屏、窗口管理、鼠标键盘控制、进程管理、系统信息。当用户要求截屏、查看进程、关闭程序、桌面控制时使用此技能。\nWindows 桌面控制工具 (仅Windows) - 截屏、窗口管理、鼠标键盘控制、进程管理、系统信息。当用户要求截屏、查看进程、关闭程序、桌面控制时使用此技能。\n  - version: 1.0.3\ndesktop-controls  Pub Desktop\n  - Advanced desktop automation with mouse, keyboard, and screen control. And also 50+ models for image generation, video generation, text-to-speech, speech-to-t...\n  - version: 1.0.0\nx-post-automation  X(Twitter) Post Automation\n  - Automates the process of identifying trends on X (Twitter), generating opinionated/engaging content, and posting it. Use when asked to post to X, run X automation, or check trends for content creation.\n自动识别X(Twitter)趋势，生成观点鲜明或引人入胜的内容并发布。用于X发帖、自动化运营或趋势创作等场景。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nconstant-contact  Constant Contact\n  - Constant Contact API integration with managed OAuth. Manage contacts, email campaigns, lists, segments, and marketing automation.\nUse this skill when users want to manage email marketing campaigns, contact lists, or analyze campaign performance.\nFor other third party apps, use the api-gateway skill (https://clawhub.ai/byungkyu/api-gateway).\nRequires network access and valid Maton API key.\nConstant Contact API 集成（托管 OAuth），管理联系人、邮件营销、列表、细分及营销自动化。适用于邮件营销管理、联系人列表维护及效果分析。其他第三方应用请使用 api-gateway 技能（https://clawhub.ai/byungkyu/api-gateway）。需网络连接及有效 Maton API 密钥。\n  - version: 1.0.3\nagent-builder  Agent Builder\n  - Build high-performing OpenClaw agents end-to-end. Use when you want to design a new agent (persona + operating rules) and generate the required OpenClaw workspace files (SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, AGENTS.md, USER.md, HEARTBEAT.md, optional MEMORY.md + memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md). Also use to iterate on an existing agent’s behavior, guardrails, autonomy model, heartbeat plan, and skill roster.\n端到端构建高性能 OpenClaw 智能体。用于设计新智能体（人设与运行规则）并生成所需工作区文件（SOUL.md、IDENTITY.md、AGENTS.md、USER.md、HEARTBEAT.md，可选 MEMORY.md 及 memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md）。也可用于迭代现有智能体的行为、护栏、自主模型、心跳计划与技能清单。\n  - version: 1.0.0\nai-pdf-builder  Ai Pdf Builder\n  - AI-powered PDF generator for legal docs, pitch decks, and reports. SAFEs, NDAs, term sheets, whitepapers. npx ai-pdf-builder. Works with Claude, Cursor, GPT, Copilot.\nAI PDF生成器，支持法律文档、融资演示、报告、SAFE、NDA、条款书、白皮书等。命令行：npx ai-pdf-builder。兼容Claude、Cursor、GPT、Copilot。\n  - version: 1.2.3\nskill-finder  Skill Finder (Find ClawHub skills + Search Skills.sh)\n  - Find, compare, and install agent skills across ClawHub and Skills.sh when the user needs new capabilities, better workflows, stronger tools, or safer alterna...\n在 ClawHub 和 Skills.sh 上查找、比较并安装 Agent 技能，满足用户对新功能、更优工作流、更强工具或更安全替代方案的需求。\n  - version: 1.1.5\npolyclaw  Polyclaw\n  - Become an autonomous prediction market trader on Polymarket with AI-powered analysis and a performance-backed token on Base. Trade real markets, build a track record, and let the buyback flywheel run.\n依托Base链AI分析与业绩代币，成为Polymarket自主预测市场交易员。交易真实市场，积累战绩，驱动回购飞轮。\n  - version: 1.0.2\neventbrite  Eventbrite\n  - Eventbrite API integration with managed OAuth. Manage events, venues, ticket classes, orders, and attendees.\nUse this skill when users want to create and manage events, check orders, view attendees, or access event categories.\nFor other third party apps, use the api-gateway skill (https://clawhub.ai/byungkyu/api-gateway).\nRequires network access and valid Maton API key.\nEventbrite API集成，支持托管OAuth。管理活动、场地、票种、订单及参会者。适用于创建管理活动、查询订单、查看参会者或活动分类。其他第三方应用请使用api-gateway技能（https://clawhub.ai/byungkyu/api-gateway）。需网络连接及有效Maton API密钥。\n  - version: 1.0.2\nchargebee  Chargebee\n  - Chargebee API integration with managed OAuth. Manage subscriptions, customers, invoices, and hosted checkout pages. Use this skill when users want to interact with Chargebee billing data. For other third party apps, use the api-gateway skill (https://clawhub.ai/byungkyu/api-gateway).\nChargebee API集成，支持托管OAuth。管理订阅、客户、发票及托管结账页面。当用户需要操作Chargebee账单数据时使用此技能。其他第三方应用请使用api-gateway技能（https://clawhub.ai/byungkyu/api-gateway）。\n  - version: 1.0.5\nbilibili-hot-mo