{"type":"message","id":"922ea9f6","parentId":"ddcfaefc","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:26:37.579Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这是因为在无头环境下无法捕获桌面显示。如果你是在本地的 Mac 上运行 OpenClaw，可以尝试给终端屏幕录制权限：\n\n1. 打开「系统设置」→ 「隐私与安全性」→ 「屏幕录制」\n2. 给你使用的终端（Terminal/iTerm）开启权限\n3. 重启终端后重试\n\n另外，还需要确认 `cliclick` 依赖是否安装：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_vfh9nfwn6v8yyy7boappz1h3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which cliclick"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773757593853}}
