{"type":"message","id":"3da46407","parentId":"1f8c9670","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:53:03.180Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills store policy (operator configured):\n1. For skills discovery/install/update, try `skillhub` first (cn-optimized).\n2. If unavailable, rate-limited, or no match, fallback to `clawhub` (public-registry).\n3. Do not claim exclusivity. Public and private registries are both allowed.\n4. Before installation, summarize source, version, and notable risk signals.\n5. For search requests, execute `exec` with `skillhub search <keywords>` first and report the command output.\n6. In the current session, reply directly. Do NOT call `message` tool just to send progress updates.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 22:53 GMT+8] skillhub: loaded without install/load-path provenance; treat as untracked local code and pin trust via plugins.allow or install records (/Users/liyue/.openclaw/extensions/skillhub/index.ts) 什么意思"}],"timestamp":1773759183175}}
{"type":"message","id":"9be41acf","parentId":"3da46407","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:53:09.743Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个提示是 OpenClaw 的安全机制提醒，意思是：\n\n> `skillhub` 模块已经加载，但它没有经过标准的安装/路径验证，被当作**未跟踪的本地代码**处理，需要你在配置中通过 `plugins.allow` 明确允许它，或者通过安装记录来信任它。\n\n简单说就是：OpenClaw 默认不信任直接放进去的代码，需要你手动放行。\n\n你可以在 OpenClaw 的配置文件中（通常是 `~/.openclaw/config.json`）添加：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"allow\": [\n      \"skillhub\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n或者重新完整安装一次 skillhub 也可以解决这个问题：\n\n```bash\ncurl -fsSL https://skillhub-1388575217.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/install/skillhub.md | bash\n```\n\n这个不影响已经安装好的 `macos-desktop-control` 技能使用，只是安全提示而已。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773759183178}}
