{"type":"message","id":"912a9b95","parentId":"5a04a10a","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:58:02.583Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"还是遇到了 `could not create image from display` 错误。这个问题的原因是：\n\n**当前 OpenClaw 运行环境无法访问 macOS 的图形显示**，所以截不了屏。\n\n如果你是在本地 Mac 上通过终端运行 OpenClaw，请确认：\n\n1. ✅ 已经开启 **屏幕录制权限**：系统设置 → 隐私与安全性 → 屏幕录制 → 勾选你的终端\n2. ✅ 已经开启 **辅助功能权限**：系统设置 → 隐私与安全性 → 辅助功能 → 勾选你的终端\n3. 🔄 开启权限后**必须重启终端**才能生效\n\n如果这些都做了还是不行，那就是因为你在用 Terminal.app 之外的方式运行（比如 VSCode 内置终端），部分版本会受限。\n\n我们来验证一下文件是否生成：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_u99g9ft95zf8s1moazi6cebb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -lh /tmp/claw_view.png 2>/dev/null || echo \"No screenshot file generated\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773759469307}}
